@AppointmentApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5164

### Get all appointments
GET {{AppointmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/appointments
Accept: application/json

###

### Get appointment by id
GET {{AppointmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/appointments/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create new appointment
POST {{AppointmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Team Meeting",
  "description": "Weekly team sync meeting",
  "startTime": "2024-10-15T10:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2024-10-15T11:00:00Z",
  "location": "Conference Room A",
  "attendeeEmail": "team@example.com",
  "status": "Scheduled"
}

###

### Update appointment
PUT {{AppointmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/appointments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Team Meeting - Updated",
  "description": "Weekly team sync meeting - Updated agenda",
  "startTime": "2024-10-15T14:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2024-10-15T15:00:00Z",
  "location": "Conference Room B",
  "attendeeEmail": "team@example.com",
  "status": "Confirmed"
}

###

### Delete appointment
DELETE {{AppointmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/appointments/1

###

